title: I Wanna Know if She is My Daughter
itunes:title: I Wanna Know if She is My Daughter
description:
Good morning Steve and Shirley I recently came back in contact with a female that I was dealing with and found out that she had a daughter that's 21. So I started asking her questions and she got real defensive. So I just came out and asked was she my daughter. And she said no.
